  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD TO YOUR WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1629734567\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCORD</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A DAY IN SPACE</h2><br><strong>Live a space adventure on board of \"Space Colony,\" a high tech space station sent to colonise the newly discovered Planet Omega in 2040.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/d3c9efb79c069e323e75972c0b1aafda.poster.avif?t=1629734567\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/d3c9efb79c069e323e75972c0b1aafda.webm?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/d3c9efb79c069e323e75972c0b1aafda.mp4?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><br>In this interactive, space exploration experience you will:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore the giant \"Space Colony I\" Space Station;<br></li><li> Carry out your daily tasks;<br></li><li> Interact with your crewmates, getting to know their personal stories;<br></li><li> Find out about the reasons behind mankind's first space colonisation;<br></li><li> Gather all the clues to find out about the staggering truth behind your cremates' deaths.</li></ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/03a118847115fbffe6a80418686f8f59.poster.avif?t=1629734567\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/03a118847115fbffe6a80418686f8f59.webm?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698400/extras/03a118847115fbffe6a80418686f8f59.mp4?t=1629734567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In-game Icons Credits:<br>Icons made by Freepik from ",
